values: well, with being told that i "should write stuff too", here it is.  blah...thats all i got to describe this hell i am stuck in.  my father (who i have never had the best of relationships with) is giving me the cold shoulder...which i know i should not be complaining about, but...grrrrrr....hes pissed cause i finally got the balls (you know what i mean) to tell him where he can put that big ego of his.  and to make things worse, my grandfather in california had triple by-pass surgery...and my grandmother was in a car accident leaving the hospital after visiting him..so, mom is down in california taking care of her parents...my referee is gone and i don't know if i am gonna be able to restrain myself from killing him....find out on in the next issue of "i am woman, hear me bitch"...:D
